Tá»ŠCH CHÃNH PHá»¦ VIá»†T NAM DÃ‚N CHá»¦ Cá»˜NG HOÃ€</font></p> <p align=\"JUSTIFY\"> 	<i><font color=\"#0000ff\" face=\"Times New Roman\">Chiá»ƒu theo quyáº¿t nghá»‹ cá»§a Há»™i Ä‘á»“ng ChÃ­nh phá»§ ngÃ y 26 thÃ¡ng 11 nÄƒm 1945 vá» viá»‡c phÃ¡t hÃ nh giáº¥y báº¡c Viá»‡t Nam;</font></i></p> <p align=\"JUSTIFY\"> 	<i><font color=\"#0000ff\" face=\"Times New Roman\">Chiá»ƒu theo quyáº¿t nghá»‹ cá»§a Há»™i Ä‘á»“ng ChÃ­nh phá»§ ngÃ y 12 thÃ¡ng 9 nÄƒm 1947,</font></i></p> <p align=\"JUSTIFY\"> 	<i><font color=\"#0000ff\" face=\"Times New Roman\">Sau khi Ban ThÆ°á»ng trá»±c Quá»‘c há»™i Ä‘Ã£ thoáº£ thuáº­n;</font></i></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">&#160;</font></p> <p align=\"CENTER\"> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"2\">RA Sáº®C Lá»†NH&#58;</font></b></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 1</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Nay thiáº¿t láº­p má»™t ngÃ¢n hÃ ng cá»§a Quá»‘c gia gá»i lÃ  Viá»‡t Nam Quá»‘c gia ngÃ¢n hÃ ng.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 2</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Viá»‡t Nam Quá»‘c gia ngÃ¢n hÃ ng cÃ³ Ä‘á»™c quyá»n phÃ¡t hÃ nh giáº¥y báº¡c.</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Giá»›i háº¡n sá»‘ báº¡c phÃ¡t hÃ nh vÃ  Ä‘iá»u kiá»‡n phÃ¡t hÃ nh sáº½ do sáº¯c lá»‡nh áº¥n Ä‘á»‹nh, sau khi Ban thÆ°á»ng trá»±c Quá»‘c há»™i thoáº£ thuáº­n.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 3</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Viá»‡t Nam quá»‘c gia ngÃ¢n hÃ ng cÃ³ nhiá»‡m vá»¥&#58;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">1- Giá»¯ nhÆ°ng kim khÃ­ quÃ½ giÃ¡ cho quá»‘c gia;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">2- LÃ m má»™t ngÃ¢n hÃ ng cho ngÃ¢n khá»‘ quá»‘c gia;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">3- Cho ChÃ­nh phá»§ vay Ä‘á»ƒ cáº¥p vá»‘n cho cÃ¡c tá»• chá»©c kinh doanh cá»§a Quá»‘c gia.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 4</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Viá»‡t Nam quá»‘c gia ngÃ¢n hÃ ng cÃ³ Ä‘á»™c quyá»n lÃ m viá»‡c há»‘i Ä‘oÃ¡i tiá»n tá»‡.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 5</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">NgoÃ i ra, Viá»‡t Nam quá»‘c gia ngÃ¢n hÃ ng cÃ³ thá»ƒ lÃ m má»i cÃ´ng viá»‡c cá»§a má»™t ngÃ¢n hÃ ng.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 6</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Viá»‡t Nam quá»‘c gia ngÃ¢n hÃ ng gá»“m cÃ³&#58;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">1- Má»™t cÆ¡ quan Ä‘iá»u khiá»ƒn vÃ  quáº£n trá»‹ gá»i lÃ  ban giÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">2- Má»™t cÆ¡ quan kiá»ƒm soÃ¡t gá»i lÃ  ban kiá»ƒm soÃ¡t.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 7</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Ban giÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c gá»“m cÃ³&#58;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">1- Má»™t Tá»•ng giÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">2- Hai phÃ³ giÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">3- vÃ  cÃ¡c giÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c cÃ¡c ngÃ nh hoáº¡t Ä‘á»™ng cá»§a quá»‘c gia ngÃ¢n hÃ ng (tá»« bá»‘n Ä‘áº¿n sÃ¡u ngÆ°á»i).</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 8</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Nhiá»‡m vá»¥ cá»§a ban giÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c lÃ &#58;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">1- Äá» nghá»‹ lÃªn chÃ­nh phá»§, qua Bá»™ TÃ i chÃ­nh, chÃ­nh sÃ¡ch vÃ  chÆ°Æ¡ng trÃ¬nh hoáº¡t Ä‘á»™ng cá»§a ngÃ¢n hÃ ng;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">2- Thá»±c hiá»‡n nhá»¯ng káº¿ hoáº¡ch Ä‘Æ°á»£c chÃ­nh phá»§ duyá»‡t y;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">3- Trá»±c tiáº¿p Ä‘iá»u khiá»ƒn cÃ´ng viá»‡c cá»§a quá»‘c gia ngÃ¢n hÃ ng.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 9</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Tá»•ng GiÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c Ä‘iá»u khiá»ƒn viá»‡c quáº£n trá»‹ vÃ  phá»¥ trÃ¡ch thi hÃ nh quyáº¿t nghá»‹ cá»§a Ban GiÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c.</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Tá»•ng GiÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c cÃ³ hai PhÃ³ Tá»•ng GiÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 10</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Ban kiá»ƒm soÃ¡t gá»“m cÃ³&#58;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">1- Má»™t Tá»•ng Thanh tra;</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">2- vÃ  tá»« hai Ä‘áº¿n bá»‘n Thanh tra.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 11</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Ban kiá»ƒm soÃ¡t cÃ³ nhiá»‡m vá»¥ kiá»ƒm soÃ¡t káº¿ toÃ¡n, ngÃ¢n quá»¹ vÃ  má»i cÃ´ng viá»‡c quáº£n trá»‹ cá»§a Quá»‘c gia NgÃ¢n hÃ ng.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u12</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">CÃ¡c nhÃ¢n viÃªn nÃ³i trong Ä‘iá»u 7 vÃ  Ä‘iá»u 10 do sáº¯c lá»‡nh bá»• nhiá»‡m theo Ä‘á» nghá»‹ cá»§a Bá»™ trÆ°á»Ÿng Bá»™ TÃ i chÃ­nh.</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Má»™t nhÃ¢n viÃªn khÃ´ng thá»ƒ vá»«a tham dá»± Ban GiÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c vá»«a tham dá»± ban kiá»ƒm soÃ¡t.</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Cháº¿ Ä‘á»™ cá»§a cÃ¡c viÃªn chá»©c nÃ y sáº½ do má»™t sáº¯c lá»‡nh quy Ä‘á»‹nh sau.</font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Cháº¿ Ä‘á»™ cÃ¡c viÃªn chá»©c khÃ¡c giÃºp viá»‡c trong Quá»‘c gia ngÃ¢n hÃ ng sáº½ do má»™t nghá»‹ Ä‘á»‹nh cá»§a Bá»™ trÆ°á»Ÿng Bá»™ TÃ i chÃ­nh quy Ä‘á»‹nh Ä‘á» nghá»‹ cá»§a Tá»•ng GiÃ¡m Ä‘á»‘c Quá»‘c gia NgÃ¢n hÃ ng.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 13</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Má»™t nghá»‹ Ä‘á»‹nh cá»§a Bá»™ TÃ i chÃ­nh sáº½ quy Ä‘á»‹nh chi tiáº¿t tá»• chá»©c Quá»‘c gia NgÃ¢n hÃ ng.</font></p> <p> 	<b><font face=\"Times New Roman\" size=\"4\">Äiá»u 14</font></b></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\">Ã”ng Bá»™ trÆ°á»Ÿng Bá»™ TÃ i chÃ­nh chiá»ƒu sáº¯c lá»‡nh thi hÃ nh. </font></p> <p> 	<font face=\"Times New Roman\